nodes.title: Final prompt preview
widgets_values: Anime-style video of a female character with long white hair and pointed ears, sitting on a tall, metal tower. She is wearing a black and white outfit with a high collar and long sleeves. The background features a dramatic, orange and blue sky with fluffy clouds. The character has a serious expression and is looking off into the distance. The lighting is dramatic, casting shadows and highlights on her body. The style is detailed and vibrant, with a focus on the character's form and expression. Slow and small Movements. Idle Animation
